snippet.title: Just Another Platformer Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Just Another Platformer, as the name suggests, is all about jumping and running as best as you can. But don't forget, having fun is important too!

Thank you for watching the trailer. 
Please leave your feedback and get the demo on 

Itch.io: https://just-another-indie.itch.io/justanotherplatformer

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3138890/Just_Another_Platformer/

Discord: https://discord.gg/xErdJp86
